    "long_instructions": "### Live Coding\r\n\r\nAryanna is preparing her live DJ set and decided to organize her code so there are multiple loops that all play together. This makes it easier to play tracks with different lengths.\r\n\r\nRight now, Aryanna is just preparing her tracks. Can you help Aryanna organize the sounds into loops so they all start and stop at the end of measure 8? Listen to the example to hear what this should sound like!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/711dcbd24f98a6f1b0013377548c3d66-image-1742398905172.png)",
